  "details": "A vulnerability was detected in Sanluan PublicCMS 5.202506.d. The affected element is the function getSignKey of the file publiccms-core/src/main/java/com/publiccms/logic/component/config/SafeConfigComponent.java. The manipulation of the argument privatefile_key results in use of hard-coded cryptographic key\n . The attack can be executed remotely. The exploit is now public and may be used. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.",
